data.eml:eml: Description of a new species of the genus Paraedes (Diptera: Culicidae) in Assam, India

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Natarajan, R. (2019): Description of a new species of the genus Paraedes (Diptera: Culicidae) in Assam, India. Zootaxa 4691 (3): 286-292, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4691.3.9
